        "id": 9571,
        "title": "Nesting Conditionals",
        "type": "practiceLevel1",
        "lessons": [
          {
            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 84793,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Time to create functions that take decisions. As a first step, let's see how to nest conditional statements inside functions.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "One Indent",
            "id": 84801,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We know that functions are blocks of code. That means nested instructions are surrounded by braces and have extra space on the left side.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"displayMessage\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"message\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(message);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"displayMessage(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Approved&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"34\" /><option startIndex=\"58\" endIndex=\"59\" /><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"57\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Approved\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>{</code>, followed by <code>console.log(message);</code>, and finally <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Braces and spaces",
            "id": 84797,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>We can add other code blocks inside a function. When we do that, the extra pair of braces let us know which instructions belong where.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isRentingAge\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"age\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"21\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Approved&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isRentingAge(\" /><text value=\"26\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"75\" endIndex=\"76\" /><option startIndex=\"77\" endIndex=\"78\" /><option startIndex=\"27\" endIndex=\"28\" /><option startIndex=\"45\" endIndex=\"46\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Approved\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>{</code> followed by <code>{</code> and then <code>}</code>, <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Indenting the entire block",
            "id": 84800,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>The space to the left is called <strong>indentation</strong>. When we add a code block inside another, the entire code block gets indented by one space.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"displayAlarm\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"time\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (time === \" /><text value=\"&quot;7:00&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Waky waky&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"displayAlarm(\" /><text value=\"&quot;7:00&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"31\" endIndex=\"53\" /><option startIndex=\"56\" endIndex=\"81\" /><option startIndex=\"83\" endIndex=\"84\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Waky waky\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>if (time === \"7:00\") {</code>, followed by <code>console.log(\"Waky waky\");</code>, and finally <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Code blocks",
            "id": 84796,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Wrapping <code>if</code> statements inside functions helps us organize and reuse our code. Now, we can use the same <code>if</code> statement with a function call.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isRentingAge\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"age\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"21\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Approved&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isRentingAge(\" /><text value=\"26\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"80\" endIndex=\"92\" /><option startIndex=\"92\" endIndex=\"93\" /><option startIndex=\"93\" endIndex=\"95\" /><option startIndex=\"95\" endIndex=\"96\" /><option startIndex=\"96\" endIndex=\"97\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Approved\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>isRentingAge</code> followed by <code>(</code> and then <code>26</code>, <code>)</code>, <code>;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Multiple instructions",
            "id": 85787,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Instructions outside of nested code blocks still get executed, even if the code inside the conditional statement gets skipped.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isRentingAge\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"age\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"21\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Approved&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Check Complete&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isRentingAge(\" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Check Complete\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: One indent",
            "id": 85825,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>What happens when we add an <code>if</code> statement inside a function?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">We're adding a code block inside another code block</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">The function will skip the <code>if</code> block when called</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">We're adding a code block inside another code block.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Braces and spaces",
            "id": 85824,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>How many instructions outside the <code>if</code> statement does this function have?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isRentingAge\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"age\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"21\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Approved&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Check done&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isRentingAge(\" /><text value=\"15\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Check done\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">One display statement</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">None, all instructions are part of the <code>if</code> statement</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">One display statement.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Indenting the entire block",
            "id": 85826,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>What's the space to the left of a nested instruction called?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Indentation</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">A code block</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick Indentation.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Code blocks",
            "id": 85827,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Why is wrapping conditionals inside functions useful?</p><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">It helps us organize and reuse our code</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">It's not, it's the same as rewriting an <code>if</code> statement every time we need it</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">It helps us organize and reuse our code.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Question: Multiple instructions",
            "id": 85828,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Which display statement executes when calling <code>isLying(false)</code>?</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isLying\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"boolean\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Welcome to the Lie Detector 3000&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (boolean === \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;He's lying&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isLying(\" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"Welcome to the Lie Detector 3000\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"He's lying\" /></content></output></code><selection iscode=\"false\" multiple=\"multiple\"><item value=\"1\" correct=\"true\">Both display statements execute</item><item value=\"2\" correct=\"false\">Only the second display statement executes</item></selection><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Both display statements execute.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: One Indent",
            "id": 85830,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nest the <code>if</code> statement inside the function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"hasPassed\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"score\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (score &gt;= \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Passed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"hasPassed(\" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"27\" /><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option startIndex=\"74\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"76\" endIndex=\"77\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>{</code> followed by <code>{</code> and then <code>}</code>, <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Braces and spaces",
            "id": 85831,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Display only <code>\"Checking Score\"</code> in the console by placing it outside the <code>if</code> statement.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"hasFailed\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"score\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Checking Score&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (score &lt;= \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Failed&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"hasFailed(\" /><text value=\"80\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"41\" endIndex=\"57\" /><option startIndex=\"94\" endIndex=\"102\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Checking Score\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>\"Checking Score\"</code>, followed by <code>\"Failed\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Indenting the entire block",
            "id": 85832,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Display both messages in the console.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"isLying\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"boolean\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (boolean === \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;He's not lying&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Done&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"isLying(\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"122\" endIndex=\"126\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"false\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"He's not lying\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Done\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Code blocks",
            "id": 85833,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Increase <code>salary</code> by 500 if it's less than 2100. Display <code>salary</code> at the end of the function.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"displaySalary\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"salary\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (salary &lt; \" /><text value=\"2100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  salary = salary + \" /><text value=\"500\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(salary);\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"displaySalary(\" /><text value=\"2000\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"57\" endIndex=\"79\" /><option startIndex=\"84\" endIndex=\"104\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2500\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>salary = salary + 500;</code>, followed by <code>console.log(salary);</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Example: Multiple instructions",
            "id": 85834,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Reduce the <code>salary</code> by 500 only if it is greater than 2100.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"function\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"getTaxedSalary\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"salary\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\") \" /><text value=\"{\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (salary &gt; \" /><text value=\"2100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  salary = salary - \" /><text value=\"500\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" }\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" salary;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" income = getTaxedSalary(\" /><text value=\"2100\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(income);\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"46\" endIndex=\"47\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"===\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"2100\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Make sure to pick <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          }
        ]
      }
